ntered the Paris Olympics as an outside medal hope after struggling with form and an injury concern recently, but based on his history, there will always begreat expectation that follow in his wake.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 391, \"end\": 403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chad le Clos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"an outside medal hope\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"form\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 482}, {\"ngram\": \"an injury concern\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"his history\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"expectation\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"his wake\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Le Clos introduced himself to the world at the 2012 Olympic Games in London where he beat American icon Michael Phelps in the 200m butterfly, before also claiming the 100m fly silver medal.\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.376552978392866e-11, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 695, \"end\": 703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9996907702885873, \"rank\": 0.00030407852243324423, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score