"ngram\": \"the second heat\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1126}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, there was some concern as he could be seen holding his shoulder and grimacing after the race, with the 32-year-old having come into the Olympics carrying an injury.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some concern\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"his shoulder\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"an injury\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was subsequently confirmed that had had not done enough to qualify for the Men's 100m Butterfly semi-finals, finishing with the 24th fastest time across the five heats.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Men's 100m Butterfly semi\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"the 24th fastest time\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"the five heats\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, he will make a disappointing exit from the Olympics, but he will always hold a special place in the history of the Games.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"a disappointing exit\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"a special place\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview published on theTeam SAwebsite, Le Clos reflected on his prolific career which has also included winning five medals at the 2010 Youth Olympics, followed by five at that year's Commonwealth Games.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1815, \"end\": 1833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.7703435736077751, \"rank\": 0.2981190849016523, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Commonwealth_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"SAwebsite\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1668}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Clos\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"his prolific career\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"five medals\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2010 Youth Olympics\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always wanted to go down as the best.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Have I under-achieved?\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have over-achieved.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us play this back.\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From 2012 I over-achieved.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I beat Phelps.\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1988, \"end\": 1994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999997918180487, \"rank\": 2.081819312237226e-07, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://d